{"tid":500684,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"疑家事困擾 25歲仔墮樓亡","createTime":"2017-12-16T04:45:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-16T05:04:18.000Z","uid":41404,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"95286b7b6e7e972b27b101d4a3ea9d24a04396dc","tid":500684,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T04:45:17.000Z","msg":"【11：10更新】新增動新聞<br />\n<br />\n凌晨零時許，黃大仙東頭邨安東樓，一名姓蔡25歲男子從高處墮下，倒臥一樓簷篷昏迷，20歲胞妹發現報警。消防及救護員到場，將事主救下送院，惜搶救終於不治。其後有3名女親友趕到醫院，聞悉死訊傷心痛哭。<br />\n警方經初步調查，未有撿獲遺書，但獲悉事主因家庭問題困援，當中包括其父親疑因有酗酒問題，事主曾為此而感到不開心。<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20171216/57587762\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171216%2F57587762&d=UQDAp1wca%2FgJo0Q%2BgRQ5aghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=9f888d18\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171216%2F57587762&h=8572b74c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20171216/57587762</a>"},{"pid":"fe598ffb9d7ce019b6493447f1738d3484e43c6b","tid":500684,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T04:49:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"487fa5201392b8078746051dc1ced0eae67a2da0","tid":500684,"uid":1833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T04:51:35.000Z","msg":"又嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9159223057d30254cd8613ce1854cc8e2f2201dc","tid":500684,"uid":149324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T04:52:32.000Z","msg":"個個都25歲"},{"pid":"8e5687412f00f3196e2bd5bd0207050a11936b63","tid":500684,"uid":76776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0